ISLAMABAD, Apr 7 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan has conveyed his best wishes and prayers for the early recovery and good health of British Prime Minister Boris Johnson.
The prime minister, in a letter to Prime Minister Boris Johnson, also underscored the importance of Pakistan and the United Kingdom working together to overcome the formidable challenges posed by COVID-19 and building a safer world.
